</sentra-tools>
Constraints:
- aiName must be chosen from: {{allowed_list}}
- Each step uses exactly one tool and includes draftArgs (required-only).
{{require_line}}
- Do NOT use Markdown code fences; do NOT output multiple <sentra-tools> blocks.
- Output only the block, no extra text.
